    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>⚠️ 注意：本游戏目前仅提供英文版本。</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>由于游戏文本以回合制节奏呈现，您可以轻松使用翻译工具（如 DeepL、截图翻译插件或OCR辅助工具）来逐步理解内容，无需担心节奏过快。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>感谢您的理解与支持，祝您游戏愉快！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085660/extras/02b96fb9e1807749f025f5a797ea617c.poster.avif?t=1768110471\" width=600 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085660/extras/02b96fb9e1807749f025f5a797ea617c.webm?t=1768110471\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085660/extras/02b96fb9e1807749f025f5a797ea617c.mp4?t=1768110471\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >认识戴夫（Dave），一名普通的办公室职员。他也许有点太常盯着窗外发呆，但总体来说，他喜欢自己的工作，也乐于和同事打趣。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >然而一切开始崩塌，他被分配到了一个前同事的工位——那位同事据说曾精神崩溃。自此，奇怪的事情接连发生。乔安娜为什么总把她的房门反锁？书桌抽屉里怎么会有一本关于恶魔学的论述？那条通向偏僻小巷的捷径尽头，究竟隐藏着什么？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085660/extras/12d420339ecc11eabaf3517cc71ffd49.poster.avif?t=1768110471\" width=600 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085660/extras/12d420339ecc11eabaf3517cc71ffd49.webm?t=1768110471\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085660/extras/12d420339ecc11eabaf3517cc71ffd49.mp4?t=1768110471\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《SIDE ALLEY》延续了姊妹作品《PSYCHOLOG》的独特风格，将沉浸式视觉小说的叙事魅力与第一人称点击互动玩法巧妙结合。<br>通过与同事的深入交流，获取他们的信任与帮助；细致调查周围环境，寻找解除诅咒的关键线索；而在某些时刻，唯一的生存之道，可能就是逃离……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085660/extras/147645fc70fc3ba029440010196969ef.poster.avif?t=1768110471\" width=600 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085660/extras/147645fc70fc3ba029440010196969ef.webm?t=1768110471\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085660/extras/147645fc70fc3ba029440010196969ef.mp4?t=1768110471\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >故事发生在一个压抑的都市环境中，这里天空鲜少可见，充满了“后室”风格的阴暗空间与令人不安的氛围。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着诅咒逐渐加深，游戏独特的视觉风格也不断施加精神压力，使玩家仿佛被卷入一场比死亡更可怕的命运之中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这座城市如同一座迷宫。你早就隐约察觉到了这一点——只是过去从未有时间去尝试不同的道路。而现在，你别无选择。</p>",
